One Button Workout uses apple's speech recognition technology, to let users easily input their workout information.
Hold record, say the exercise you have completed, and you are done.
Our algorithm picks out the important data and saves it so there is no time spent fumbling with text fields or pen and paper.
The user can easily browse their past workouts and see charts and graphs interpreting all their past data.
See your personal bests, total weight lifted, calories burned by day, week, or month.
One button workout makes logging your exercises easy, quick and rewarding, making you feel good about your progress and leaving you more time to workout.
